{
  "page": "Dragonstone (material)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Dragonstone</b> is a building material used by the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">Valyrians</a> in much of their construction. It is harder than <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Steel\" title=\"Steel\">steel</a>, granite or <a href=\"/index.php/Diamond\" title=\"Diamond\">diamond</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is believed the Valyrians used <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magic</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonflame\" title=\"Dragonflame\">dragonflame</a> to work the stone, turning it into liquid before shaping and fusing it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_roads\" title=\"Valyrian roads\">dragonroads</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> the inner walls of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Wall\">Black Wall</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and the ruins of a <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian</a> fort in <a href=\"/index.php/Naath\" title=\"Naath\">Naath</a> are all made of fused black dragonstone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_naath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_naath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragonstone_(material)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_seven_kingdoms:_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Seven Kingdoms: The Reach: Oldtown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Volantis.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Doom of Valyria.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reach: Oldtown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: The Quarrelsome Daughters: Myr, Lys, and Tyrosh.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_naath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_naath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: Naath.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=